					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">For one thing, get your controller reading out of NMI.
<br />NMI code should be about rapidly consuming data you build into buffers during rendering time.
<br />
<br />Or do it the easy way and turn off the screen before you write your data there, then turn it back on when the next frame begins.</div>

					
