						<div class="postbody">You can force blanking by writing zero to $2001, but only do that when rewriting the entiere screen or if you're doing heavy updates that cannot be done any other way.
<br />
<br />Otherwise, you'd just want to update your stuff at VBlank time (at the start of the NMI routine) and make sure it does take shorter than the VBlank time.</div>

					
